nd%20averages%20just%20around%2050.%20Can%20you%20drop%20him%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20understood%20that%20seniors%20like%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20along%20with%20pace%20spearhead%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20will%20now%20focus%20on%20ODIs%20and%20Tests%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20season%20with%20nine%20WTC%20Tests%20between%20September%202024%20to%20January%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20schedule%20includes%20two%20home%20games%20each%20against%20Bangladesh%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20five%20away%20against%20Australia%20and%20the%20marquee%20ODI%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20will%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20new%20players%20in%20T20Is%20including%20IPL%20stars%2C%20the%20likes%20of%20Rinku%20Singh%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20Avesh%20Khan%2C%20and%20Khaleel%20Ahmed%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20travel%20to%20Zimbabwe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20Hardik%20Pandya%20and%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20are%20not%20rested%2C%20they%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20the%20designated%20captain%20and%20vice-captain%20for%20the%20tour%20although%20both%20have%20been%20playing%20constantly%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718769600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fdcn9g7qo_gambhir-and-iyer-bcci_625x300_19_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fend-of-exile-for-shreyas-iyer-report-makes-big-claim-for-indias-future-matches-5917278%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Gambhir's%20expected%20appointment%20as%20India's%20head%20coach%20could%20provide%20a%20new%20lease%20of%20life%20to%20IPL%20champion%20skipper%20Shreyas%20Iyer's%20international%20career%20during%20the%20three-match%20ODI%20series%20against%20Sri%20Lanka.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fend-of-exile-for-shreyas-iyer-report-makes-big-claim-for-in