harset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66723ede2efa138e0330f5cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Boeing%20737%20plane%20landing%20in%20Australia.%3Cp%3EJames%20D.%20Morgan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20report%20from%20the%20Senate%20subcommittee%20contains%20fresh%20allegations%20from%20a%20Boeing%20whistleblower.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESam%20Mohawk%2C%20a%20quality%20assurance%20investigator%2C%20says%20the%20737%20program%20lost%20track%20of%20hundreds%20of%20bad%20parts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBoeing's%20CEO%2C%20however%2C%20said%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%20he%20remains%C2%A0%26quot%3Bproud%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20company's%20safety%20record.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Senate%20subcommittee%20investigating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffaa-investigated-boeings-safety-culture-and-the-results-arent-great-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoeing's%20safety%20and%20quality%20practices%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20released%20a%20new%20report%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20contains%20new%20allegations%20from%20company%20whistleblowers%20about%20what%20happens%20to%20faulty%20plane%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hsgac.senate.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024.06.17-PSI-Majority-Staff-Memorandum.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esprawling%20204-page%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20contained%20several%20new%20allegations%20from%20whistleblowers%20familiar%20with%20the%20company's%20practices%20at%20its%20Washington%20facilities.%20The%20allegations%20%26quot%3Bpaint%20a%20troubling%20picture%20of%20a%20company%20that%20prioritizes%20speed%20of%20manufacturing%20and%20cutting%20costs%20over%20ensuring%20the%20quality%20and%20safety%20of%20aircraft%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20subcommittee%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20slate%20of%20accusations%20came%20from%20Sam%20Mohawk%2C%20a%20Boeing%20quality%20assurance%20investigator%20in%20Renton%2C%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMohawk%2C%20per%20the%20committee's%20report%2C%20wrote%20a%20June%2011%20complaint%20to%20the%20Occupational%20Safety%20and%20Health%20Administration%20alleging%20that%20the%20737%20program%20was%20losing%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%26quot%3B%20of%20%26quot%3Bnon-conforming%26quot%3B%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMohawk%20further%20alleged%20that%20at%20the%20Renton%20factory%2C%20the%20company%20ordered%20staff%20to%20move%20%26quot%3Bimproperly%20stored%26quot%3B%20aircraft%20parts%20to%20%26quot%3Bintentionally%20hide%26quot%3B%20them%20from%20FAA%20inspectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20approximately%2060%20parts%20being%20stored%20outdoors%2C%20including%2042%20rudders%20alone%2C%20plus%20flaps%2C%20winglets%2C%20ailerons%2C%20stabilizers%2C%20and%20vertical%20fins%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohawk's%20OSHA%20complaint%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20then%2C%20those%20parts%20that%20were%20hidden%20from%20the%20FAA%20inspection%20have%20been%20moved%20back%20to%20the%20outside%20area%20or%20lost%20completely%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohawk%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Senate%20subcommittee%20also%20highlighted%20allegations%20from%20former%20Boeing%20quality%20manager%20Merle%20Meyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeyers%2C%20a%20former%20Boeing%20quality%20manager%2C%20said%20staff%20at%20Boeing's%20manufacturing%20team%20regularly%20tried%20to%20retrieve%20bad%20parts%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Breclamation%26quot%3B%20area%20even%20after%20they%20were%20sent%20there%20for%20disposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeyers%20further%20alleged%20that%20Boeing's%20manufacturing%20staff%20had%20forms%20that%20helped%20them%20justify%20moving%20parts%20from%20reclamation%20back%20into%20the%20production%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20example%20forms%20reviewed%20by%20the%20Subcommittee%2C%20some%20dating%20as%20far%20back%20as%202002%2C%20appeared%20to%20relate%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20small%20and%20large%20aircraft%20parts%2C%20including%20%26quot%3B787%20leading%20edge%20slats%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Blanding%20gear%20fitting%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3B787%20nacelle%20forgings%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bwire%20bundles%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20subcommittee%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fresh%20slate%20of%20accusations%20from%20Boeing%20whistleblowers%20adds%20to%20the%20existing%20allegations%20against%20the%20company%20from%20other%20Boeing%20whistleblowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20two%20Boeing%20whistleblowers%20died%20before%20the%20Senate%20subcommittee's%20report%20came%20out%20on%20Monday.%20Former%20Spirit%20AeroSystems%20employee%20Joshua%20Dean%2C%2045%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-supplier-whistleblower-dies-after-sudden-illness-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edied%20in%20May%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20contracting%20a%20sudden%20illness.%20Dean%20had%20testified%20against%20Spirit%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2024%2F01%2F12%2F1223936777%2Fa-recent-lawsuit-alleges-excessive-defects-at-boeing-parts-supplier%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eshareholder%20lawsuit%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20accused%20it%20of%20poor%20quality%20control%20when%20producing%20the%20Boeing%20737-Max.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20Boeing%20whistleblower%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjohn-barnett-boeing-manager-whistleblower-dead-self-inflicted-wound-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EJohn%20Barnett%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2062%2C%20died%20in%20March%2C%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20his%20deposition%20against%20Boeing.%20The%20Charleston%20County%20coroner's%20office%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20former%20Boeing%20manager%20died%20from%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20self-inflicted%20gunshot%20wound.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Senate's%20new%20document%20did%20drop%20before%20B