2_blank%5C%22%3Eall-powerful%20chips%3C%2Fa%3E%20fueling%20artificial%20intelligence%20%E2%80%94%20is%20still%20high%2C%20the%20greatest%20existential%20threat%20to%20the%20company%20is%20if%20demand%20slows%20down.%20So%2C%20to%20keep%20itself%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20game%2C%20Nvidia%20has%20diversified%20its%20business%20into%20the%20world%20of%20cloud%20service%20software%20and%20rentals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Nvidia%20started%20its%20cloud%20service%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fthese-2-analysts-just-raised-their-expectations-for-nvdia---here-s-why-1032564067%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDGX%20Cloud%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20competitor%20to%20some%20of%20Nvidia's%20own%20customers%2C%20including%20Microsoft%20and%20Amazon%20Web%20Services.%20DGX%20Cloud%20rents%20Nvidia-powered%20servers%20from%20within%20AWS's%20data%20centers%20and%20then%2C%20promising%20greater%20computing%20capability%2C%20leases%20them%20back%20to%20Nvidia's%20customers%2C%20The%20Information%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20AWS%20was%20hesitant%20to%20allow%20Nvidia%20to%20set%20up%20a%20competing%20shop%20right%20under%20its%20nose%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Information.%20But%20once%20other%20rival%20companies%20agreed%20to%20the%20terms%20of%20DGX%20Cloud%2C%20AWS%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20relent%20%E2%80%94%20it%20just%20couldn't%20risk%20souring%20its%20relationship%20with%20the%20supplier%20of%20its%20crucial%20chips%2C%20per%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20told%20The%20Information%20the%20suggestion%20that%20AWS%20was%20concerned%20about%20upsetting%20Nvidia%20was%20%26quot%3Bspeculative%20and%20incorrect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said%20Amazon%20worked%20closely%20with%20Nvidia%20to%20develop%20features%20in%20the%20DGX%20Cloud%20offering%20that%20offered%20customers%20%26quot%3Bthe%20best%20of%20both%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20deep%20collaboration%20with%20Nvidia%20that%20goes%20back%20more%20than%2013%20years%2C%20when%20together%20we%20launched%20the%20world's%20first%20GPU%20cloud%20instance%20on%20AWS%2C%20and%20today%20we%20offer%20the%20widest%20range%20of%20Nvidia%20GPU%20solutions%20for%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20Amazon's%20spokesperson%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20DGX%20Cloud%2C%20Nvidia%20has%20creatively%20maneuvered%20itself%20into%20a%20position%20where%20its%20own%20customers%20are%20helping%20it%20compete%20with%20them.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-leadership-style-insiders-tough-boss-admit-mistakes-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECEO%20Jensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E's%20aggressive%20strategy%20to%20maintain%20dominance%20doesn't%20stop%20there%2C%20per%20The%20Information.%C2%A0Nvidia%20is%20also%20requiring%20customers%20to%20build%20out%20more%20space%20to%20house%20the%20GPUs%20they%20buy%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20and%20telling%20them%20how%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNvidia%20will%20not%20ship%20GPUs%20unless%20the%20customer%20can%20certify%20that%20they%20have%20data%20center%20capacity%20in%20which%20to%20place%20those%20GPUs%2C%26quot%3B%20Raul%20Martynek%2C%20who%20works%20with%20cloud%20providers%20as%20the%20CEO%20of%20DataBank%2C%20told%20The%20Information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20titan%20chipmaker%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20demanding%20its%20clients%20provide%20proof%20of%20their%20expanded%20data%20center%20capacity%2C%20is%20also%20telling%20customers%20how%20to%20design%20the%20racks%20that%20hold%20the%20servers%20and%20GPUs%20within%20those%20data%20centers%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20because%20the%20racks%20are%20specifically%20designed%20to%20fit%20Nvidia%20chips%2C%20it%20could%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20the%20customer%20to%20switch%20to%20chips%20from%20competing%20companies%20without%20incurring%20tremendous%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20Nvidia%20and%20its%20clients%20like%20Amazon%20have%20agreed%20to%20continue%20their%20somewhat%20symbiotic%20relationship%2C%20but%20that%20hasn't%20stopped%20competition%20from%20brewing%20on%20both%20sides.%20While%20Nvidia%20has%20expanded%20into%20cloud%20services%2C%20AWS%20is%20also%20developing%20its%20own%20AI%20chips%2C%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-nvidia-aws-ai-chip-dominance-gpu-trainium-inferentia-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrainium%20and%20Inferentia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20aim%20to%20compete%20with%20Nvidia's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20its%20current%20strategy%20is%20clever%20enough%20to%20have%20propelled%20Nvidia%20to%20become%20the%20world's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fnvidia-stock-price-market-cap-microsoft-most-valuable-company-ai-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20valuable%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20company's%20quest%20for%20industry%20dominance%20could%20come%20back%20to%20bite%20it.%20The%20Department%20of%20Justice%20is%20looking%20to%20launch%20an%20investigation%20into%20potential%20antitrust%20violations%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F06%2F06%2Ffederal-antitrust-probes-nvidia-microsoft-openai-00161973%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPolitico%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20feds%20are%20preparing%20to%20investigate%20whether%20Nvidia%20came%20to%20become%20the%20leading%20supplier%20of%20high-end%20semiconductors%20through%20anticompetitive%20behavior%2C%20per%20Politico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Nvidia%20declined%20to%20comment%20when%20reached%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-advantage-amazon-desperation-for