%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fgcpbl00g_priyanka-gandhi-_625x300_18_June_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20has%20finally%20relented.%20She%20has%20been%20named%20as%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20for%20the%20by-poll%20in%20Kerala's%20Wayanad.%20Ever%20since%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20entered%20politics%20in%202004%2C%20there%20has%20been%20internal%20clamour%20within%20the%20Congress%20for%20her%20induction%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20late%20Jagdish%20Piyush%2C%20a%20longstanding%20Congress%20worker%20from%20Amethi%20since%20Sanjay%20Gandhi's%20days%20in%201977%2C%20coined%20a%20slogan%20in%201999%3A%20%3Cem%3EAmethi%20ki%20danka%2C%20bitiya%20Priyanka%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Amethi's%20clarion%2C%20daughter%20Priyanka).%20That%20was%20when%20Priyanka%20first%20campaigned%20for%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20in%20neighbouring%20Raebareli.%20The%20slogan%20adorned%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20region%2C%20earning%20Piyush%20the%20moniker%20of%20the%20'Bard%20of%20Amethi'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20recently%20as%20late%20April%20this%20year%2C%20Priyanka's%20husband%2C%20Robert%20Vadra%2C%20publicly%20supported%20her%20candidacy%20when%20decisions%20on%20Congress%20candidates%20for%20Amethi%20and%20Raebareli%20were%20pending.%20He%20even%20offered%20himself%20as%20a%20candidate%20if%20she%20hesitated%20to%20step%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Strong%20Start%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20entered%20politics%20two%20decades%20ago%2C%20Priyanka%20had%20stated%20that%20her%20priority%20was%20raising%20her%20children%2C%20who%20were%20then%20very%20young.%20Her%20son%2C%20Rehan%2C%20is%20now%2023%2C%20and%20her%20daughter%2C%20Miraya%2C%20is%20a%20year%20younger.%20Priyanka%20has%20been%20actively%20involved%20in%20campaigning%20for%20her%20mother%20and%20brother%20in%20the%20past%20elections%2C%20making%20frequent%20trips%20to%20oversee%20work%20in%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20formally%20joining%20politics%20in%20January%202019%20as%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20Priyanka%20initially%20served%20as%20the%20campaign%20head%20for%20the%20party%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20though%20without%20significant%20success.%20Her%20notable%20two-day%20Ganga%20yatra%20from%20Prayagraj%20to%20Varanasi%20in%20March%202019%2C%20on%20a%20boat%2C%20garnered%20attention%20but%20not%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20role%20as%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in-charge%2C%20however%2C%20facilitated%20strong%20relationships%20with%20local%20politicians.%20Unlike%20Rahul%2C%20who%20thinks%20in%20English%20and%20translates%20while%20speaking%20in%20Hindi%2C%20Priyanka%2C%20who%20spent%20many%20hours%20in%20childhood%20at%20the%20home%20of%20acclaimed%20Hindi%20scholar%20Harivansh%20Rai%20Bachchan%2C%20is%20fluent%20in%20colloquial%20Hindi.%20This%20ability%20proved%20vital%20in%20forming%20the%20Congress-Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20alliance%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%202024%2C%20which%20posed%20a%20formidable%20challenge%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20state%20elections%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Priyanka%20emerged%20as%20a%20key%20campaigner%20for%20her%20party.%20Her%20influence%20was%20particularly%20noted%20in%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20campaign%2C%20attributed%20in%20part%20to%20her%20efforts%20alongside%20trusted%20aide%20Rajiv%20Shukla%2C%20a%20Congress%20secretary%20and%20cricket%20administrator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20campaign%2C%20Priyanka%20came%20across%20as%20someone%20who%20would%20come%20up%20with%20swift%20and%20sharp%20rebuttals%20against%20the%20BJP's%20allegations%2C%20often%20invoking%20the%20sacrifices%20of%20her%20grandmother%20and%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20Will%20See%20Me%20In%20Her%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMakhan%20Lal%20Fotedar%2C%20a%20trusted%20aide%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%20who%20oversaw%20elections%20in%20Raebareli%20from%201977%20and%20served%20as%20her%20political%20secretary%20from%201980%20to%201984%2C%20recounted%20a%20conversation%20he%20had%20with%20her%20in%20Srinagar%20on%20September%2028%2C%201984%2C%20just%20days%20before%20her%20tragic%20assassination%20on%20October%2031%2C%201984.%20Fotedar%20chronicled%20this%20conversation%20in%20his%20memoir%2C%20The%20Chinar%20Leaves%2C%20published%20in%202015.%20Indira%20Gandhi%20had%20visited%20Kashmir%20with%20her%20grandchildren%20on%20September%2027%2C%20returning%20to%20Delhi%20two%20days%20later%20before%20embarking%20on%20her%20final%20campaign%20tour%20to%20Orissa%20(now%20Odisha).%20Her%20scheduled%20interview%20with%20British%20actor%20Peter%20Ustinov%20for%20a%20TV%20channel%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20October%2031%20was%20tragically%20cut%20short%20due%20to%20her%20assassination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20events%20of%20September%2028%2C%201984%2C%20Fotedar%20writes%20that%20Indira%20Gandhi%20visited%20the%20shrine%20of%20the%20Kuldevi%20of%20the%20Nehru%20clan%2C%20Sharika%20Bhagwan%20Ashtadash%20(goddess%20with%2018%20hands)%20at%20Hariparvat%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20dargah%20of%20Sufi%20saint%20Makhdoom%20Sahib.%20%26quot%3BReturning%20to%20her%20guest%20house%2C%20she%20said%20something%20remarkable%20about%20herself%20and%20her%20granddaughter%2C%26quot%3B%20Fotedar%20writes.%20%26quot%3BFotedarji%2C%20I%20may%20not%20live%20long.%20But%20you%20must%20watch%20over%20Priyanka%20as%20she%20grows.%26quot%3B%20Fotedar%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20think%20I%20will%20live%20that%20long%3F%26quot%3B%20To%20this%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20replied%20affirmatively%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20will%20live%20to%20see%20her%20grow%20and%20shine%20on%20the%20national%20horizon.%20People%20will%20see%20me%20in%20her%20and%20remember%20me%20when%20they%20see%20her.%20She%20will%20shine%20and%20the%20next%20century%20will%20be%20hers.%20Then%20people%20will%20forget%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFotedar%20passed%20away%20in%20September%202017.%20It%20is%20uncertain%20whether%20the%20majority%20of%20Indians%20today%2C%20born%20after%20her%20assassination%2040%20years%20ago%2C%20remember%20Indira%20Gandhi%20apart%20from%20the%20enduring%20legacy%20of%20the%20liberation%20of%20Bangladesh%20in%20December%201971%20and%20the%20unforgettable%20memory%20of%20the%20Emergency%20imposed%2049%20years%20ago%20in%20June.%20However%2C%20as%20Priyanka%20makes%20her%20electoral%20debut%2C%20this%20conversation%20recorded%20by%20Fotedar%20is%20worth%20recalling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201990%2C%20I%20asked%20Fotedar%20whether%20he%20had%20shared%20his%20recollections%20with%20Rajiv%20Gandhi.%20He%20confirmed%20that%20he%20had%20and%20that%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20had%20inquired%2C%20%26quot%3BDid%20Mummy%20really%20say%20so%3F%26quot%3B%20Later%2C%20after%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20entry%20into%20politics%20and%20the%20popularisation%20of%20Jagdish%20Piyush's%20slogan%2C%20%3Cem%3EAmethi%20Ka%20Danka%2C%20bitiya%20Priyanka%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Fotedar%20formally%20wrote%20to%20her%2C%20citing%20the%20conversation.%20It%20did%20not%20receive%20a%20reply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20Priyanka%20Reignite%20The%20Spirit%20Of%20Debate%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Priyanka%20wins%20in%20Wayanad%2C%20she%20will%20become%20the%20sole%20woman%20MP%20from%20Kerala%2C%20a%20state%20that%20has%20a%20rich%20legacy%20of%20women's%20role%20in%20society.%20Announcing%20her%20candidature%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20reiterated%20her%202022%20statement%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3ELadki%20hoon%2C%20Lad%20sakti%20hoon%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(I%20am%20a%20woman%2C%20I%20can%20fight).%20If%20elected%2C%20Priyanka%20will%20hopefully%20reintroduce%20spirited%20debates%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20While%20occasionally%20echoing%20Rahul's%20discordant%20rhetoric%2C%20her%20discourse%20has%20largely%20been%20in%20line%20with%20what%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20%3Cem%3Esarsanghchalak%3C%2Fem%3E%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20recently%20described%20as%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EPaksh-Pratipaksh%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20spirit%20of%20debate-meaning%2C%20opposition%20not%20just%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20team%20of%2099%20MPs%20includes%20promising%20figures%20who%20comfortably%20won%20in%20closely%20contested%20polls%3A%20Deepender%20Hooda%20(Rohtak%2C%20Haryana)%2C%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20(Jorhat%2C%20Assam)%2C%20Rakibul%20Hussain%20(Nagaon%2C%20Assam)%2C%20Manish%20Tiwari%20(Chandigarh)%2C%20Geniben%20Thakor%20(Sabarkantha%2C%20Gujarat)%2C%20Varsha%20Gaikwad%20(Mumbai%20North%20Central%2C%20Maharashtra)%2C%20Vishal%20Patil%20(Sangli%2C%20Maharashtra)%2C%20Praniti%20Shinde%20(Solapur%2C%20Maharashtra)%2C%20Rajesh%20Rathore%20(Sitapur%2C%20UP)%2C%20and%20Thiruvananthapuram's%20four-term%20MP%2C%20Shashi%20Tharoor.%3Cbr%3E%5CnRahul%20Gandhi's%20decision%20on%20whether%20to%20accept%20the%20position%20of%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20is%20awaited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Priyanka%20wins%20in%20Wayanad%2C%20one%20of%20the%20prominent%20Lok%20Sabha%20faces%20from%20the%20opposition%20may%20once%20again%20be%20a%20woman%2C%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20days%20of%20Sushma%20Swaraj%2C%20who%20had%20led%20the%20BJP's%20spirited%20opposition%20during%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718764320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fgcpbl00g_priyanka-gandhi-_625x300_18_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2