20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-weighs-in-on-the-chaos-gripping-his-newspaper-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718756526000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66721228087acd2be9b4e019%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-weighs-in-on-the-chaos-gripping-his-newspaper-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jeff%20Bezos%20assured%20Washington%20Post%20journalists%20the%20paper%20would%20maintain%20its%20journalistic%20standards%20as%20controversies%20mount%20over%20CEO%20Will%20Lewis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40businessinsider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A336%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-weighs-in-on-the-chaos-gripping-his-newspaper-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Post%20Malone%20Sets%20August%20Release%20Date%20for%20New%20Album%2C%20%E2%80%98F-1%20Trillion%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718756319000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGettyImages-1192241776.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236041984%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Post%20Malone%E2%80%99s%20sixth%20studio%20album%20%E2%80%9CF-1%20Trillion%E2%80%9D%20will%20arrive%20on%20Aug.%2016%2C%20the%20American%20singer%20and%20rapper%20announced%20Tuesday.%20Malone%20shared%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20sign%20in%20Nashville%20revealing%20the%20album%E2%80%99s%20title%20and%20car-themed%20logo.%20In%20the%20caption%20he%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CSup%20motherfuckas%E2%80%A6F-1%20Trillion%20August%2016th.%E2%80%9D%20The%20digital%20billboard%E2%80%99s%20location%20is%20a%20hint%20on%20what%20could%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Thania%20Garcia%2