anjith%20Ramasamy's%20mind%20immediately%20traveled%20further%20south%2C%20to%20another%20blood-pumping%20organ%2C%20one%20that%20he%20knows%20very%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPenis%20being%20such%20a%20vascular%20organ%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20heart%2C%20we%20said%2C%20'Hey%2C%20could%20this%20also%20be%20present%20in%20the%20penis%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamasamy%2C%20a%20reproductive%20urology%20specialist%20who%20has%20conducted%20penile%20implant%20surgeries%20in%20Miami%20for%20many%20years%2C%20wondered%20how%20the%20microplastics%20that%20we%20inadvertently%20inhale%20from%20everyday%20items%20including%20food%2C%20water%20bottles%2C%20and%20household%20dust%2C%20might%20impact%20fertility%20and%20verility%20in%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20he's%20found%2C%20while%20still%20preliminary%2C%20is%20that%20microplastics%20are%20present%20in%20some%20penises%20experiencing%20erectile%20dysfunction%20(ED).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d10e2f89-ecd2-42ac-a0b3-26bd0bbf4c43%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMicroplastics%20were%20found%20in%2080%25%20of%20penises%20with%20ED%20in%20this%20small%20study%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222035%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22plastic%20bottles%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6671e7d82efa138e0330daff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221473%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMost%20of%20the%20microplastic%20found%20in%20penises%20was%20the%20kind%20that's%20used%20to%20manufacture%20plastic%20bottles.%20%3Cp%3EPeter%20Dazeley%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERamasamy's%20first-of-its-kind%20study%2C%20just%20released%20in%20the%20International%20Journal%20of%20Impotence%20Research%2C%20was%20a%20small%2C%20pilot%20sample%20of%20six%20men%2C%20all%20with%20ED%2C%20each%20one%20undergoing%20surgery%20to%20insert%20a%20penile%20implant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20study%20is%20still%20preliminary%2C%20it's%20part%20of%20a%20growing%20body%20of%20research%20that%20finds%20microplastics%20are%20present%20everywhere%20in%20the%20human%20body%20that%20researchers%20have%20looked%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20one%20of%20the%20first%20studies%20to%20study%20a%20connection%20between%20impotence%20and%20more%20plastic%20use.%20Other%20studies%20have%20already%20suggested%20there%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhealthymale.org.au%2Fhealth-article%2Fdo-plastics-our-food-and-environment-affect-male-fertility%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emay%20be%20some%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20our%20plastic%20modern%20existence%20and%20lower-quality%20sperm.%20Ramasamy%20wanted%20to%20know%20whether%20microplastics%20might%20physically%20impact%20penis%20muscle%20function.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20each%20surgery%2C%20Ramasamy%20carefully%20extracted%20some%20tissue%20from%20deep%20inside%20the%20shaft%20of%20the%20penis%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cancer.gov%2Fpublications%2Fdictionaries%2Fcancer-terms%2Fdef%2Fcorpus-spongiosum%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20area%20that's%20responsible%20for%3C%2Fa%3E%20making%20and%20sustaining%20erections.%20He%20and%20his%20team%20worked%20to%20ensure%20there%20was%20no%20plastic%20contamination%20in%20the%20surgery%20rooms%20by%20using%20non-plastic%20surgical%20instruments%20and%20collecting%20the%20tissue%20in%20glass%20containers.%20They%20then%20whisked%20the%20tissue%20off%20to%20two%20separate%20labs%20for%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScientists%20found%20microplastics%20present%20in%20five%20of%20the%20six%20penises%20they%20sampled.%20The%20most%20abundant%20plastic%20in%20the%20penises%20was%20polyethylene%20terephthalate%2C%20or%20PET%2C%20a%20common%20plastic%20used%20in%20food%20packaging%20including%20plastic%20bottles%20and%20takeout%20containers.%20They%20also%20found%20polypropylene%2C%20which%20is%20used%20to%20make%20plastic%20bottle%20caps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b12a6895-c0f9-4901-829a-51b66a3af1b1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20are%20gobbling%20up%20more%20plastics%20than%20ever%2C%20and%20learning%20more%20about%20the%20effects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22takeout%20food%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6671e85c087acd2be9b4ca0d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMost%20takeout%20containers%20are%20lined%20with%20plastic%20coating%20(yes%2C%20even%20the%20cardboard%20ones.)%3Cp%3Efiladendron%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20know%20how%20much%20plastic%20might%20be%20hiding%20out%20in%20the%20penises%20of%20men%20without%20ED%20and%20can't%20take%20much%20away%20from%20such%20a%20small%20initial%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20this%20research%20goes%20hand%20in%20hand%20with%20what%20other%20microplastics%20experts%20are%20discovering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubs.acs.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1021%2Facs.est.4c00010%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsuming%20more%20plastic%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20ever%20before.%20In%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1056%2FNEJMoa2309822%3Flogout%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%3C%2Fa%3E%20microplastic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhsc.unm.edu%2Fnews%2F2024%2F05%2Fhsc-newsroom-post-microplastics-testicular.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20younger%20men%20have%20had%20more%20microplastic%20in%20them%20than%20older%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20man%20in%20this%20study%20who%20didn't%20have%20any%20detectable%20microplastics%20in%20his%20penis%20%26quot%3Bleads%20a%20very%20traditional%2C%20Cuban%20guy%20elderly%20lifestyle%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramasamy%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20said%20he%20doesn't%20use%20a%20lot%20of%20plastics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20not%20getting%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20takeout%20that%20often%20comes%20in%20plastic-lined%20containers%2C%20and%20he's%20not%20drinking%20from%20plastic-lined%20coffee%20cups%20or%20plastic%20water%20bottles%20very%20often.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20without%20trying%2C%20he's%20doing%20most%20of%20the%20things%20that%20microplastic%20researchers%20recommend%20to%20people%20hoping%20to%20reduce%20their%20risk%20of%20any%20potential%20microplastic-related%20health%20issues%3A%20avoiding%20drinking%20and%20eating%20from%20plastic%2C%20and%20never%20microwaving%20plastic%20containers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20finding%20has%20given%20Ramasamy%20pause.%20He%20has%20become%20much%20more%20wary%20of%20drinking%20from%20plastic%20water%20bottles%20since%20completing%20this%20study%2C%20and%20he%20tries%20to%20always%20put%20his%20food%20on%20a%20real%20plate%20now%20before%20he%20re-heats%20it%2C%20instead%20of%20microwaving%20plastic%20tubs.%20He%20knows%20it's%20still%20unclear%20what%20contribution%20microplastics%20might%20be%20making%20to%20infertility%20and%20low%20sperm%20quality%2C%20but%20he's%20got%20a%20hunch%20there's%20probably%20some%20contribution%2C%20on%20some%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20convenient%20as%20society%20has%20become%2C%20I%20think%20we're%20facing%20some%20of%20these%20harms%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20our%20parents%20were%20exposed%20to%20as%20much%3A%20They%20were%20not%20drinking%20water%20out%20of%20plastic%20bottles%20%E2%80%94%20they%20were%20certainly%20not%20doing%20as%20much%20takeout.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c081f96-1909-4cea-8163-d7d04064973c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECould%20microplastics%20be%20interfering%20with%20important%20penis%20muscles%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22penis%20enlargement%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F608850593f0560001881c522%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMicroplastics%20could%20impact%20smooth%20muscle%20function%2C%20Ramasamy%20suggested.%3Cp%3ECarol%20Yepes%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicroplastics-found-in-human-testicles-what-to-do-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicroplastics%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20traveled%20to%20almost%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20body%20that%20scientists%20have%20looked%20at%20so%20far%2C%20including%20lungs%2C%20livers%2C%20blood%20vessels%2C%20penises%2C%20and%20brains%2C%20as%20well%20as%20fluids%20including%20semen%2C%20blood%2C%20and%20placentas.%20Just%20last%20month%2C%20researchers%20at%20the%20University%20of%20New%20Mexico%20found%20microplastics%20in%20testicles%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F36948312%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecementing%20the%20idea%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20microplastics%20can%20penetrate%20the%20body's%20protective%20blood-testes%20barrier.%20What%20these%20tiny%20bits%20of%20plastic%20are%20doing%20to%20our%20bodies%20remains%20an%20open%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichard%20Pilsner%2C%20a%20men's%20reproductive%20health%20expert%20at%20Wayne%20State%20University%20who%20studies%20the%20chemicals%20in%20plastics%2C%20says%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20learn%20in%20terms%20of%20where%20it's%20accumulating%20and%20what%20processes%20it%20may%20be%20affecting.%26quot%3B%20Recent%20work%20he's%20done%20suggested%20that%20men%20with%20higher%20levels%20of%20plasticizers%20and%20plastic%20chemicals%20in%20their%20bodies%20see%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factor.niehs.nih.gov%2F2023%2F6%2Ffeature%2F3-mens-reproductive-epigenetics%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esperm%20age%20faster%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20a%20similar%20way%20to%20cigarette%20smokers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20kind%20of%20is%20all%20pointing%20in%20the%20same%20direction%20%E2%80%94%20that%20these%20environmental%20factors%20are%20influencing%20sperm%20fitness%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20impact%20of%20microplastics%20on%20erections%20is%20unclear%2C%20that's%20nothing%20new%20in%20this%20field.%20Erections%20are%20still%20a%20very%20poorly%20understood%2C%20multifactorial%20phenomenon%2C%20involving%20nerves%2C%20hormones%2C%20muscles%2C%20and%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamasamy%20is%20confident%20that%20this%20is%20seriously%20worth%20investigating%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20recent%20link%20between%20more%20microplastics%20in%20blood%20vessels%20pumping%20oxygen%20to%20the%20brain%2C%20and%20more%20heart%20attacks%20and%20strokes.%20Couldn't%20it%20also%20be%20the%20case%20that%20microplastics%20are%20connected%20to%20erection%20issues%2C%20in%20a%20similar%2C%20physical%20way%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20could%20have%20good%20blood%20supply%2C%20but%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20actual%20muscle%20to%20do%20the%20heavy%20lifting%2C%20how%20are%20you%20going%20to%20make%20it%20work%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicroplastics-found-in-penis-muscles-for-the-first-time-study-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718755261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6671f2daa76074d191cd2983%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicroplastics-found-in-penis-muscles-for-the-first-time-study-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Scientists%20are%20suspicious%20that%20there%20might%20be%20a%20connection%20between%20fewer%20erections%20and%20more%20plastic%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20early.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hbrueck%40businessinsider.com%20(Hilary%20Brueck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicroplastics-found-in-penis-muscles-for-the-first-time-study-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A