%20that%20contains%20a%20hefty%20dose%20of%20SPF%2036.%20It's%20fragrance-free%2C%20dye-free%2C%20and%20hypoallergenic%2C%20so%20this%20is%20a%20great%20pick%20for%20those%20with%20sensitive%20skin.%20In%20addition%20to%20sun-blocking%20zinc%20oxide%20and%20octinoxate%2C%20you'll%20get%20free%20radical-fighting%20antioxidants%2C%20including%20vitamin%20C%20ester%20and%20vitamin%20E.%20An%20added%20benefit%20of%20this%20lip%20balm%20is%20that%20it's%20water%20resistant%20for%20up%20to%2080%20minutes%2C%20so%20you'll%20be%20well%20prepared%20for%20the%20next%20trip%20to%20the%20beach%20or%20the%20ski%20slopes.%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20my%20favorite%20and%20highly%20recommended%20lip%20balms%20is%20EltaMD's%20UV%20Broad-Spectrum%20Lip%20Balm%20with%20SPF%2031.%20Its%20creamy%2C%20long-lasting%20moisturization%20soothes%20the%20lips%20and%20provides%20a%20protective%20barrier%20from%20UV%20rays%2C%20leaving%20your%20lips%20hydrated%20and%20healthy%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20Levine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20drugstore%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20this%20lip%20sunscreen%20ointment%20because%20I'm%20never%20without%20Aquaphor's%20ultra-nourishing%20Lip%20Repair.%20The%20two%20products%20have%20similar%20ingredient%20lists%20and%20consistencies.%20And%20though%20I'm%20not%20a%20huge%20fan%20of%20the%20sunscreen%20smell%20and%20taste%2C%20they're%20minimal%20and%20do%20not%20override%20the%20efficacy%20of%20this%20balm.%20The%20formula%20specifically%20caters%20to%20those%20with%20sensitive%20skin%2C%20and%20I%20find%20this%20to%20be%20true%2C%20as%20well.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EKatie%20Decker-Jacoby%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20former%20style%20%26amp%3B%20beauty%20reviews%20fellow%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20moisturizing%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20know%20Jack%20Black%20as%20the%20popular%20men's%20skincare%20line%2C%20but%20this%20lip%20balm%20is%20for%20everyone.%20The%20colorless%20formula%20contains%20antioxidant-rich%20vitamin%20E%20and%20green%20tea%2C%20plus%20SPF%2025%2C%20and%20goes%20on%20thick%20without%20feeling%20heavy%20or%20greasy.%20A%20perk%20of%20this%20lip%20balm%20is%20that%20you%20can%20choose%20from%20several%20flavors%2C%20my%20favorite%20being%20the%20popular%20Mint.%20On%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20there%20isn't%20a%20ton%20of%20product%20in%20the%20squeeze-tube%20container%2C%20but%20that%20also%20means%20it's%20easy%20to%20stash%20in%20a%20handbag%20or%20jacket%20pocket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20mineral%3Cp%3ESupergoop!%20excels%20at%20making%20sun-protective%20products%20more%20akin%20to%20skincare%20than%20the%20typical%20sticky%20sunscreen.%20Now%2C%20it's%20added%20lipstick%20to%20that%20list%20with%20this%20smooth%20and%20hydrating%20formula%20containing%20shea%20butter%2C%20natural%20mango%2C%20peptides%2C%20and%20SPF%2030.%20I%20appreciate%20that%20it's%20pigment-packed%2C%20combining%20the%20benefits%20of%20a%20lip%20balm%20with%20SPF%20and%20lipstick%20to%20simplify%20your%20makeup%20routine.%20While%20there%20are%20currently%20five%20shades%20made%20to%20flatter%20a%20variety%20of%20skin%20tones%2C%20from%20a%20vibrant%20coral%20to%20a%20deep%20plum%2C%20it%20would%20be%20great%20to%20see%20even%20more%20options.%20Another%20plus%20for%20this%20lip%20product%20is%20that%20it%20has%20a%20mineral%20formula.%20Dr.%20Levine%20adds%20that%20%26quot%3BSupergoop's%20products%20focus%20on%20safe%20ingredients%20(avoiding%20parabens%20and%20synthetic%20fragrances%20often%20found%20in%20other%20lipsticks%20and%20associated%20with%20health%20risks).%20I've%20used%20this%20lip%20product%20and%20find%20it%20to%20be%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20sensitive%20lips%3Cp%3EDr.%20Levine%20names%20this%20as%20one%20of%20the%20best%20lip%20balms%20with%20SPF%2C%20recommending%20it%20for%20those%20who%20have%20sensitive%20skin.%20She%20adds%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bprovides%20UVB%2FUVA%20protection%20and%20is%20paraben%20free%20and%20water-resistant%2C%20making%20it%20ideal%20for%20lips%20receiving%20extreme%20sun%20exposure.%26quot%3B%20A%20nice%20perk%20of%20this%20sunblock%20stick%20is%20that%20it%20can%20be%20used%20on%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20face%20or%20to%20cover%20moles%20on%20other%20body%20parts%20more%20precisely%2C%20though%20that%20does%20mean%20lip-balm-sized%20tubes%20will%20go%20fast.%20Because%20it's%20a%20solid%20formula%2C%20you%20can%20look%20forward%20to%20a%20mess-free%20application%20to%20areas%20like%20lips%2C%20nose%2C%20and%20under-eyes%20while%20on%20the%20move.%20Dr.%20Levine%20also%20recommends%20looking%20for%20SPF%20levels%20of%2030%20or%20higher%2C%20which%20this%20pick%20far%20surpasses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20scented%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20is%20sensitive%20to%20the%20sun%20and%20prone%20to%20my%20fair%20skin%20burning%2C%20I'm%20especially%20cautious%20with%20the%20products%20I'm%20using.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20I%20use%20SPF%20just%20about%20everywhere%2C%20even%20in%20the%20colder%20winter%20months.%20I%20absolutely%20swear%20by%20Palmer's%20Cocoa%20Butter%20Formula%20Lip%20Balm.%20It%20has%20SPF%2015%20and%20also%20prevents%20my%20lips%20from%20being%20chapped.%20It%20applies%20buttery%20smooth%2C%20as%20its%20name%20suggests%2C%20and%20smells%20divine.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%20Victoria%20Giardina%2C%20former%20buying%20guides%20fellow%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20all-day%20wear%3Cp%3EThe%20tube%20and%20formula%20remind%20me%20of%20old-school%20Vaseline%2C%20but%20much%20more%20protective%20and%20way%20less%20goopy.%20The%20SPF%2030%20is%20great%20for%20protecting%20my%20lips%20and%20the%20formula%20includes%20shea%20butter%20for%20lots%20of%20moisture.%20It%20doesn't%20contain%20any%20oxybenzone%2C%20octinoxate%2C%20or%20octocrylene%20that%20would%20be%20harmful%20to%20coral%20reefs%2C%20so%20I%20always%20use%20this%20when%20I'm%20around%20the%20beach.%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EJada%20Wong%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20senior%20editor%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECoola%20Classic%20Liplux%20Organic%20Lip%20Balm%20Sunscreen%20SPF%2030%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20quality%20plant-based%20sunscreen%20lip%20balm%2C%20this%20one%20from%20Coola%20offers%20broad-spectrum%20protection%2C%20instant%20moisture%2C%20vitamins%2C%20and%20antioxidants.%20Plus%2C%20it's%20water-resistant%20for%2080%20minutes%20and%20should%20be%20reapplied%20every%20two%20hours.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mariehayagmd.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Hayag%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20good%20balm%20that%20provides%20broad-spectrum%20protection%20against%20UV%20rays%20while%20also%20providing%20hydration%20to%20the%20lips%20through%20ingredients%20like%20jojoba%20and%20avocado%20oil.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20glossy%3Cp%3EFor%20days%20when%20you%20want%20more%20color%20and%20luster%2C%20this%20lip%20gloss%20checks%20off%20those%20boxes%20%E2%80%94%20plus%2C%20it%20has%20broad-spectrum%20SPF%2035%20sun%20protection.%20You%20can%20reapply%20every%20two%20hours%2C%20but%20every%2040%20minutes%20if%20you're%20swimming%20or%20sweating%20a%20lot.%20According%20to%20Dr.%20Hayag%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20great%20gloss%20that%20contains%20zinc%20oxide%20and%20Vitamin%20E%20to%20aid%20in%20photoprotection.%20It%20also%20contains%20hyaluronic%20acid%2C%20helping%20the%20lips%20stay%20well%20moisturized.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20has%20peptides%20that%20give%20the%20lips%20a%20more%20plump%20appearance.%26quot%3B%20The%20shade%20selection%20includes%20rose%2C%20pink%2C%20champagne%2C%20coral%2C%20and%20clear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20tinted%3Cp%3EThis%20tinted%20lip%20balm%20has%20a%20gentle%2C%20cruelty-free%2C%20and%20reef-safe%20formula%20that%20does%20all%20of%20that%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20fends%20off%20ultraviolet%20rays%2C%20too.%20The%20broad-spectrum%20SPF%2030%20sheer%20tinted%20balm%20comes%20in%20red%2C%20pink%2C%20and%20nude.%20According%20to%20Dr.%20Hayag%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20also%20has%20multiple%20ingredients%20in%20it%20to%20help%20keep%20your%20lips%20moisturized%2C%20like%20avocado%20oil%20and%20olive%20butter.%20The%20balm%20also%20contains%20shea%20butter%2C%20which%20is%20rich%20in%20antioxidants%20and%20soothes%20and%20softens%20the%20lips.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFAQs%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20SPF%20and%20what%20SPF%20should%20I%20wear%20on%20my%20lips%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESPF%20stands%20for%20sun%20protection%20factor%2C%20which%20is%20the%20measure%20of%20how%20well%20a%20certain%20formula%20will%20protect%20you%20from%20the%20sun's%20rays.%C2%A0%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20if%20you%20use%20an%20SPF%2030%20product%20properly%2C%20it%20would%20take%20you%2030%20times%20longer%20to%20burn%20than%20if%20you%20used%20no%20sunscreen%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Hale%20explains.%20The%20Skin%20Cancer%20Foundation%20recommends%20SPF%2015%20for%20daily%20wear%20and%20SPF%2030%20for%20prolonged%20outdoor%20activity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat's%20the%20difference%20between%20UVA%20and%20UVB%20rays%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20ultraviolet%20A%20(UVA)%2C%20which%20is%20connected%20with%20skin%20aging%2C%20and%20ultraviolet%20B%20(UVB)%2C%20which%20is%20linked%20to%20burning.%20Instead%20of%20worrying%20about%20whether%20your%20lip%20balm%20protects%20against%20UVA%20or%20UVB%20rays%2C%20Dr.%20Hale%20says%20to%20pick%20broad-spectrum%20sunscreen%20products%2C%20as%20they%20shield%20your%20skin%20from%20both%20rays.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20can%20sun%20damage%20do%20to%20your%20lips%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20skin%20on%20your%20lips%20is%20thinner%20and%20missing%20a%20layer%20that%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20body%20uses%20for%20UV%20protection%2C%20so%20it's%20more%20susceptible%20to%20burning.%20Too%20much%20sun%20exposure%20without%20any%20protective%20lip%20balm%20can%20lead%20to%20dryness%2C%20flakiness%2C%20and%20even%20skin%20cancer.%20Dr.%20Hale%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BAbout%2090%20percent%20of%20nonmelanoma%20skin%20cancers%20are%20associated%20with%20exposure%20to%20UV%20radiation%20from%20the%20sun.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20there%20certain%20ingredients%20I%20should%20look%20out%20for%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Dr.%20Hale%2C%20there%20are%20two%20groups%20of%20UV-blocking%20ingredients%3A%20physical%20and%20chemical.%20The%20former%20are%20ingredients%20like%20zinc%20oxide%20and%20titanium%20dioxide%2C%20while%20the%20latter%20includes%20components%20like%20avobenzone%20and%20octisalate.%20%26quot%3BLook%20for%20products%20with%20antioxidants%20like%20vitamin%20E%20and%20vitamin%20C%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Hayag%20says.%20%26quot%3BThey%20neutralize%20and%20boost%20protection%20from%20free%20radicals%20produced%20by%20UV%20radiation%20and%20visible%20light.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20ingredients%20to%20avoid%2C%20Dr.%20Hayag%20explains%20that%20products%20with%20menthol%20%E2%80%94%20the%20thing%20that%20gives%20cough%20drops%20and%20pain%20relief%20creams%20its%20cooling%20effect%20%E2%80%94%20can%20irritate%20the%20lips.%20You%20should%20also%20stay%20away%20from%20phenol%20and%20fragrance%20for%20the%20same%20reason.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhen%20should%20I%20wear%20it%20and%20how%20often%20should%20I%20apply%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20experts%20urge%20you%20to%20wear%20lip%20balm%20with%20SPF%20both%20outdoors%20and%20indoors%2C%20as%20the%20sun%20can%20penetrate%20glass%20windows.%20They%20suggest%20reapplying%20every%20two%20hours%20but%20more%20frequently%20if%20you're%20eating%2C%20drinking%2C%20or%20swimming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20should%20I%20do%20if%20my%20lips%20get%20sunburnt%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Hale%20recommends%20the%20following%20steps%3A%20move%20into%20a%20shady%20spot%2C%20stay%20hydrated%2C%20take%20Advil%20or%20Motrin%20to%20reduce%20inflammation%20and%20apply%20a%20water-based%2C%20moisturizing%20lip%20product.%20For%20the%20very%20last%20step%2C%20she%20advises%20steering%20clear%20of%20petroleum%20and%20oil-based%20balms%20that%20could%20possibly%20aggravate%20the%20burn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-lip-balm-spf%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718741155000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F604148992dc90100183557a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-lip-balm-spf%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wearing%20sunscreen%20is%20crucial%2C%20but%20we%20often%20forget%20to%20apply%20it%20to%20our%20lips.%20We%20consulted%20dermatologists%20to%20determine%20the%20best%20lip%20balms%20with%20SPF.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aphillips%40businessinsider.com%20(Ashley%20Phillips%2CKatie%20Decker-Jacoby)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-lip-balm-spf%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Richa%20recalls%20impromptu%20solo%20trip%20to%20Amsterdam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718740757000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111093881%2Cimgsize-51394.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmom-to-be-richa-chadha-recalls-her-impromptu-solo-trip-to-amsterdam-cant-just-up-and-leave-now-anymore-na%2Farticleshow%2F111093857.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111093857.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERicha%20Chadha%20is%20in%20the%20final%20stages%20of%20her%20pregnancy%2C%20spending%20time%20at%20home%20with%20husband%20Ali%20Fazal%2C%2