abha%20elections%2C%20down%20from%20its%202019%20tally%20of%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tally%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20manifestation%20of%20the%20people's%20disapproval%20of%20the%20political%20shake-up%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20and%20the%20BJP's%20role%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tremors%20had%20started%20with%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20breaking%20ranks%20with%20the%20NDA%20and%20joining%20hands%20with%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20the%20Congress%20after%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20the%20newly%20formed%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20could%20stake%20claim%20to%20form%20government%2C%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20made%20an%20attempt%20to%20form%20government%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20a%20few%20of%20his%20loyalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20later%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20split%2C%20pulling%20down%20the%20MVA%20government%2C%20and%20rebel%20leader%20Eknath%20Shinde%20formed%20government%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20became%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%C2%A0%20He%20had%20subsequently%20let%20slip%20that%20the%20plan%20was%20formed%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20split%20in%20the%20NCP.%20In%20both%20cases%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20awarded%20the%20party%20name%20and%20symbol%20to%20the%20rebels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20verdict%20made%20the%20people's%20disapproval%20clear.%20Both%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20won%20a%20huge%20mandate%2C%20and%20the%20Congress%20too%20benefited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20-%20allied%20with%20the%20undivided%20Sena%20led%20by%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20-%20won%2023%20of%2025%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20it%20contested%20in%20Maharashtra.%20The%20Shiv%20Sena%20contested%2023%20and%20won%2018.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20just%20nine%20seats.%20Its%20allies%20--%20the%20splinter%20units%20of