a%20during%20the%20partition.%20At%20the%20age%20of%2017%2C%20she%20was%20married%20into%20a%20Ludhiana-based%20business%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20children%20went%20to%20boarding%20school%2C%20she%20enrolled%20for%20a%20bakery%20course%20in%20Punjab%20Agriculture%20University%20and%20used%20the%20spare%20time%20to%20sharpen%20her%20cooking%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20she%20became%20popular%20for%20her%20baking%20recipes%20and%20ice-creams%20among%20her%20friends.%20She%20started%20a%20small%20business%20with%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%20300%20to%20buy%20an%20oven%2C%20and%20churned%20ice-cream%20in%20her%20own%20backyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20number%20of%20orders%20and%20unable%20to%20make%20profits%2C%20Rajni%20soon%20incurred%20losses.%20It%20was%20then%20that%20her%20husband%2C%20Dharamvir%2C%20supported%20her%20with%20Rs%2020%2C000%20to%20start%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F244880%2Frajni-bector-mrs-bectors-cremica-ipo-biscuits-sauces-bread-ice-cream-women-entrepreneur-success-story-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eice-cream%20manufacturing%20unit%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%201978.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20chose%20the%20name%20Cremica%20for%20her%20brand%20as%20it%20sounded%20similar%20to%20%E2%80%98cream%20ka%E2%80%99%20(made%20of%20cream).%20She%20started%20selling%20ice-creams%20and%20eventually%20grew%20the%20business%20into%20making%20breads%2C%20biscuits%20and%20sauces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20big%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20women%20rarely%20stepped%20into%20business%2C%20and%20she%20had%20to%20battle%20many%20naysayers.%20However%2C%20with%20her%20family%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%20she%20took%20Cremica%20to%20new%20heights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20brand%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20second%20largest%20exporter%20of%20biscuits%20with%20its%20products%20available%20in