ee-with-his-regime%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20sumo%20wrestling%20event%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20sitting%20intently%20and%20watching%20them%20train%20and%20observing%20their%20techniques%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20The%20weight%20of%20the%20occasion%20dawned%20on%20her%2C%20but%20she%20points%20out%20that%20all%20fright%20lay%20forgotten%20when%20she%20set%20foot%20in%20the%20ring%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20was%20met%20by%20thunderous%20applause.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20stadium%20was%20cheering%20for%20me%20because%20the%20announcer%20had%20mentioned%20that%20I%20had%20come%20all%20alone%20from%20India%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20tournament%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20is%20riveting%20and%20gives%20Hetal%20goosebumps.%20The%20success%20of%20this%20first%20global%20opportunity%20%E2%80%94%20she%20was%20among%20the%20top%2010%20%E2%80%94%20propelled%20her%20towards%20the%20ones%20that%20followed.%20At%20the%20World%20Games%20in%202009%2C%20she%20was%20the%20only%20female%20athlete%20from%20India%20out%20of%20200%20competing%20athletes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%20win%2C%20Hetal%20had%20to%20retire%20in%202012%20because%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20sponsorship.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20she%20underscores%20lack%20of%20support%20as%20the%20biggest%20hurdle%20that%20stops%20women%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F318867%2Ffirst-woman-indian-footballer-to-play-english-league-she-kicks-academy-underprivileged-girls-aditi-chauhan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epursuing%20sports%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20sumo%20wrestling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20few%20years%20have%20kept%20her%20on%20her%20toes%20with%20the%20documentary%20film%20%E2%80%98Sumo%20Didi%E2%80%99%2C%20directed%20by%20Jayant%20Rohatgi.%20Hetal%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%20film%20is%20essayed%20by%20Shriyam%20Bhagnani.%20And%20Hetal