2title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Took%20a%20Year%20%26amp%3B%20Many%20Lawyers%E2%80%99%3A%20A%20Gay%20Couple%E2%80%99s%20Road%20to%20Adopting%20Their%20Son%20%26amp%3B%20Living%20Their%20Dream%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Mentions%20of%20suicide%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPapa%2C%20can%20a%20boy%20and%20boy%20get%20married%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20of%20course!%20Daddy%20and%20I%20are%20married.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20about%20a%20girl%20and%20girl%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDo%20you%20both%20love%20each%20other%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESrivatsan%20looked%20through%20the%20rear-view%20mirror%20in%20the%20car%20at%20his%20husband%20Saravanan%2C%20and%20said%20a%20resounding%20%E2%80%9Cyes%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20did%20Saravanan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20glad%20you%20both%20are%20married%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20their%20son%20Sendhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20seemingly%20nonchalant%20conversation%20was%20the%20only%20one%20that%20six-year-old%20Sendhan%20needed%2C%20to%20understand%20the%20relationship%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337564%2Ffree-tiffin-service-meals-for-senior-citizens-rakesh-panchal-gujarat-donate-now%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebetween%20his%20fathers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20were%20no%20follow-up%20questions!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKids%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20inhibitions%20and%20they%20are%20not%20judgemental.%20Sendhan%20accepted%20us%20with%20open%20arms.%20He%20even%20painted%20a%20rock%20with%20the%20words%2C%20%E2%80%98My%20dads%20rock%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20presented%20it%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srivatsan%2C%20based%20out%20of%20Toronto%2C%20Canada%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnecdotes%20like%20this%20make%20one%20wish%20that%20adults%2C%20too%2C%20were%20as%20simple%20as%20children%20and%20understood%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20completely%20okay%20for%20two%20men%20or%20two%20women%20to%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20each%20other.%20Wouldn%E2%80%99t%20life%20be%20much%20simpler%20if%20adults%20started%20thinking%20the%20way%20children%20do%3F%20It%20would%20have%20definitely%20made%20the%20lives%20of%20these%20two%20men%20easier%20as%20they%20embarked%20on%20a%20journey%20from%20Chennai%20to%20Singapore%2C%20finally%20settling%20in%20Toronto%20in%20search%20of%20a%20society%20that%20accepts%20them%20for%20who%20they%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20have%20also%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20them%20or%20any%20other%20gay%20couple%20who%20wishes%20to%20adopt%20a%20child%20from%20India.%20But%20this%20couple%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20let%20any%20challenges%20deter%20them%20from%20living%20their%20best%20lives%20and%20adopting%20their%20son%2C%20who%20they%20now%20call%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20light%20of%20their%20lives%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESrivatsan%20and%20Saravanan%20went%20through%20a%20year-long%20process%20and%20spent%20over%2060%2C000%20Canadian%20dollars%20to%20legally%20adopt%20Sendhan%20as%20their%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20the%20journey%20like%20for%2045-year-old%20Srivatsan%3F%20How%20did%20he%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20being%20gay%20and%20navigating%20life%20when%20his%20parents%20wanted%20him%20to%20marry%20a%20girl%2C%20no%20matter%20what%3F%20From%20trying%20to%20take%20his%20own%20life%20to%20being%20out%20and%20proud%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20his%20incredible%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Choosing%20myself%20helped%20me%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20his%20early%20childhood%2C%20Srivatsan%20knew%20that%20he%20was%20different.%20He%20felt%20more%20comfortable%20with%20his%20cousin%20sisters%20than%20his%20brothers.%20His%20first%20crush%20was%20on%20a%20blue-eyed%20boy%20with%20curly%20hair.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CI%20