%20of%20a%20few%20members%20of%20their%20family%20at%20their%20wedding.%20Srivatsan%E2%80%99s%20mother%20walked%20him%20down%20the%20aisle%2C%20finally%20accepting%20her%20son%20for%20who%20he%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20few%20years%20were%20a%20whirlwind%20of%20happiness%20for%20the%20couple%20as%20they%20enjoyed%20wedded%20bliss.%20They%20soon%20adopted%20two%20dogs%20and%20considered%20adding%20a%20child%20to%20their%20family.%20During%20the%20same%20time%2C%20they%20found%20out%20about%20an%20accidental%20pregnancy%20of%20a%20relative%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20relative%20was%2040%20at%20the%20time%20and%20already%20had%20four%20children.%20She%20found%20out%20very%20late%20in%20the%20pregnancy.%20We%20decided%20to%20adopt%20her%20child%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Srivatsan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20adoption%20process%20was%20far%20from%20smooth%20for%20the%20couple.%20Since%20gay%20marriage%20is%20not%20legal%20in%20India%2C%20they%20had%20to%20adopt%20Sendhan%20through%20the%20Canadian%20legal%20system.%20They%20first%20brought%20Sendhan%20to%20Canada%20a%20few%20months%20before%20his%20fifth%20birthday%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20process%20was%20complicated%20because%20our%20son%20is%20an%20Indian%20citizen%20while%20I%20am%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%20and%20my%20husband%20is%20on%20his%20way%20to%20becoming%20one.%20We%20brought%20our%20son%20here%20and%20then%20started%20the%20process%20of%20adoption%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Srivatsan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20more%20than%20a%20year%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20lawyers%2C%20and%20over%2060%2C000%20Canadian%20dollars%20before%20the%20adoption%20was%20legally%20processed.%20Yet%2C%20everything%20was%20worth%20it%20as%20they%20became%20parents%20to%20a%20beautiful%2C%20inquisitive%2C%20loving%20child%2C%20they%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESeeing%20life%20in%20a%20new%20light%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20parent%20has%20been%2