%20year%20(2023-24)%20till%20February%202024%2C%20they%20earned%20revenues%20of%20Rs%202.2%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Mansi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20big%20ambition%20is%20to%20build%20the%20future%20of%20water%20and%20drive%20climate%20resilience%20by%20unlocking%20wastewater%E2%80%99s%20potential%20to%20be%20a%20key%20source%20of%20water%20globally.%20To%20do%20this%2C%20we%20intend%20to%20build%20the%20tech%20ecosystem%20for%20wastewater%20by%20not%20only%20working%20with%205%2C000%20facilities%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years%20to%20ensure%20they%20operate%20well%20but%20also%20creating%20data%20products%20that%20replace%20the%20consultant%20industry%20that%20drives%20infrastructure%20decisions%20with%20a%20more%20data-driven%20approach.%20We%20also%20intend%20to%20enable%20each%20building%20and%20factory%20to%20be%20water-neutral.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Rajesh%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20eventual%20vision%20is%20to%20create%20water-positive%20buildings%20and%20industries%20that%20in%20turn%20significantly%20improve%20quality%20of%20life%20in%20our%20cities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.digitalpaani.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDigital%20Paani%3C%2Fa%3E%2FInstagram%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fpulse%2Fdigital-paani-making-watertech-work-alexander-hogeveen-rutter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%2FAlexander%20Hogeveen%20Rutter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FBharatFounders%2Fstatus%2F1775471473580286296%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETwitter%2FBharat%20Founders%20Fund%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718116327000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%2