%20rely%20heavily%20on%20chemical%20inputs%2C%20organic%20farming%20presents%20a%20harmonious%20alternative%2C%20promising%20a%20return%20to%20eco-friendly%20practices%20without%20sacrificing%20productivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEyyo%E2%80%99s%20approach%20was%20always%20to%20stay%20abreast%20with%20the%20latest%20agricultural%20innovations%2C%20adapting%20and%20implementing%20new%20methods%20that%20could%20support%20the%20environment%20and%20yield%20healthy%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Kottayam%20resident%20made%20the%20switch%20to%20organic%20farming%20after%20relocating%20to%20Nedumkandam%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20commitment%20to%20avoid%20inorganic%20vegetables%20commonly%20available%20in%20markets.%20Starting%20with%20basic%20gardening%20using%20standard%20grow%20bags%2C%20he%20soon%20discovered%20the%20limitations%20of%20these%20products%20%E2%80%94%20they%20were%20prone%20to%20tearing%20and%20decayed%20within%20a%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20to%20find%20a%20solution%2C%20he%20embarked%20on%20a%20journey%20to%20create%20a%20better%20grow%20bag%20that%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20durable%20but%20also%20integrated%20a%20clever%20drip%20irrigation%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-2-min-1718113039.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eyyo's%20patented%20grow%20bags%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-2-min-1718113039.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-2-min-1718113039-300x135.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-2-min-1718113039-500x225.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-2-min-1718113039-768x346.jpeg%20768w%2C%2